# {{context|legal}} The [[crime]] of causing an accident, as with a motor vehicle, and leaving without acknowledging responsibility.
# {{context|baseball}} A play in baseball where the [[baserunner]]s leave their base before the batter hits the ball, assuming that the batter will in fact hit the ball and this will give them an advantage.
# {{context|military}} The military technique of attacking one place and then quickly moving to another before defenders can react.

